# 🛡️ Security Commands

```bash
sudo -l                    # Check sudo privileges
last                       # Login history
who                        # Logged-in users
passwd                     # Change password
ufw status                 # Firewall status
sudo ufw enable            # Enable firewall
sudo ufw allow 22          # Allow SSH
sudo ufw deny 80           # Block port
```

